data.description: Newly Reduced Price!!! Excellent opportunity to own a 4-bedroom 2 downstairs bathrooms home in the wonderful city of El Monte. Home features 4 bedrooms (3 bedrooms downstairs and 1 bedroom upstairs) with a balcony and inviting views of the mountains. Neighborhood is quiet and peaceful with long-standing homeowners. Home also features a living room with a cozy fireplace featuring granite hearth, Kitchen with a dining ell, granite counters and plenty of counter space. Kitchen island adding that touch of extra space to prepare dinner for your family and friends. Separate family room which leads you to the stairway to the 4th bedroom and private balcony. Wood laminate flooring. Ceiling fans in most of the home. Central air conditioning and heat. 2-car garage and vinyl fencing. New water heater. New garage door opener and new springs. Extra large driveway for your RV, boat, or families with multiple vehicles. Walking distance to Durfee elementary. Schools are excellent and have a high rating. Close to freeways and shopping.
